headline: Nordson Stock: Appeal Lures As The Premium Valuation Disappears

headline: Nordson: A Dividend Aristocrat Reinforcing Its Position Through Tuck-In Acquisitions
summary: Nordson increased its revenue from $1.7 billion in FY 2015 to $2.7 billion in FY 2024, a compound annual growth rate of 5.3%.
